metadata.name: Your Ghost
metadata.description:
I hear The whispers of your breath 
Will they haunt me til my death?

rooms fill with dust and empty frames
as time starts to erase your name 

seasons change within days
when you lose your mind 

now I see that sanity is truly hard to find 

your ghost haunts this hollow house 
and I know that I let you down
